Text:
This is more a comment on your general u/ls than this particular effort but you must be such an amazing repository of information about music from the 80s. Thanks for sharing your efforts with everyone! :)

I'm usually familiar with about 10-15% of the artists that you revive and so it's a real treat to get a broader sample of the era.
Hey Electrish, thx for the comment. I am glad i have been abke to somehow revive and keep the dark side of the 80s alive! cheers
thanks also from me,great to hear some different music. greetings from sydney australia
